õóŸOarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/book/standard_library.mdŸ@490739b1175adbe641a7d99c5f5bca44d0f7d89ca9f5d4eba5ea85eb1923fff4•prev:ë∫Standard Library (Preview)Ÿ 

Nushell ships with a standard library of useful commands written in native Nu. By default, the standard library is loaded into memory (but not automatically imported) when Nushell starts.
