::: warning Important!

``std/log``
 exports environment variables. To use the 
``std/log``
 module in your own module, please see 
[link: ./modules/creating_modules.md#export-env-runs-only-when-the-use-call-is-evaluated] this caveat
 in the "Creating Modules" Chapter.
:::
